{"tid":2489434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消息：彭定康要求首相制裁中港官員及實體    過百英議員響應","createTime":"2021-04-15T03:02:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T04:40:25.000Z","uid":227801,"like":196,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"1bb5cb574c71c22249dc12c5fd55bdaf0fca1e9b","tid":2489434,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:02:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/uk-letter-04142021220116.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fuk-letter-04142021220116.html&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sD2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=c61391bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/uk-letter-04142021220116.html</a><br />\n本台獲得的信件顯示，這過百名英國議員，要求政府引用《馬格尼茨基人權問責法》，制裁打壓香港民主運動的官員及實體，並對侵害新疆維吾爾族人權的官員，特別是新疆黨委書記陳全國作出制裁。<br />\n<br />\n2021-04-14<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n末代港督彭定康勳爵及英國103位跨黨派議員，周二（13日）聯署去信英國首相約翰遜。本台獲得的信件顯示，這過百名英國議員，要求政府引用《馬格尼茨基人權問責法》，制裁打壓香港民主運動的官員及實體，並對侵害新疆維吾爾族人權的官員，特別是新疆黨委書記陳全國作出制裁。<br />\n聯署者包括被中共制裁的保守黨前黨魁施志安（Iain Duncan Smith）、保守黨議員勞頓（Tim Loughton）及上議院議員奧爾頓勳爵（David Alton），還有工黨影子外相藍麗珊 (Lisa Nandy) 及影子亞太國務大臣金諾克（Stephen Kinnock）。<br />\n信中指出，他們就上月中共制裁英國議員表示反對，認為這顯示中共的威權主義正在擴張，並攻擊西方國家的民主代表，故有需要聯手採取強而有力的對策，包括擴大制裁名單。信中又指，中英關係所謂的「黃金時代」已經過去，他們敦促英國政府馬上重新檢視及制定全面的跨部門策略，應對中國政府對自由世界不斷加劇的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n2021年3月22日，英國聯同歐盟、美國及加拿大就北京侵犯新疆維吾爾族人權，制裁了四名新疆官員及新疆生產建設兵團公安局，英國外相藍韜文當時指，這是英國第一次制裁中國官員。<br />\n4日後，中國外交部向英國九名人士和四個團體實施「反制裁」。<br />\n被中共制裁的保守黨前黨魁施志安當時在推持回應指，「有責任就中國政府侵犯香港人權和對維吾爾人進行種族滅絕表態。如果中國將憤怒發洩到我頭上，我會戴上這枚榮譽徽章」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcTVEkYBqMt8iMfyiptbqKYhKH7RfyFzgfhFvw6zU8aXj?filename=8wqX03m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8wqX03m.png&h=3e18a627&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe638bd04b6f26c98c061c5ec76c1667632aee80","tid":2489434,"uid":77196,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:03:36.000Z","msg":"都係果句，冇連坐法效力唔大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c0d5bf383a35e66a4a77361e06d5c86ec974551","tid":2489434,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1441d6f53a912c9a2e7b1f3f396e0a319d3a4b4","tid":2489434,"uid":377617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:10:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a9caa0697621c7f1390d1f14eecddebb57a956","tid":2489434,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dbebda53379c10e61293254ad1c955f6633d0d3","tid":2489434,"uid":19725,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"fe638bd04b6f26c98c061c5ec76c1667632aee80","tid":2489434,"uid":77196,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:03:36.000Z","msg":"都係果句，冇連坐法效力唔大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:12:46.000Z","msg":"外國唔興連坐。。。唉"},{"pid":"e3ca77bea426224a004d3004039e95aa035587fd","tid":2489434,"uid":120499,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"fe638bd04b6f26c98c061c5ec76c1667632aee80","tid":2489434,"uid":77196,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:03:36.000Z","msg":"都係果句，冇連坐法效力唔大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:15:17.000Z","msg":"肥彭都係想試緊支共底線，班土匪係欺善怕惡<br />\n<br />\n支共啲官平時收得咁埋，好難玩連坐法"},{"pid":"d5c674360049d4f25efba8a4ea25eb0ea196efb9","tid":2489434,"uid":256246,"lik